milestones.description: Tony Ura and Chad Soper's 81-run partnership is PNG's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 43 between Mahuru Dai and Hiri Hiri
Tony Ura has become the top scorer for PNG in ODIs with 422 runs, going past Mahuru Dai's 383
Tony Ura has broken the record for most sixes (9) in ODIs for PNG, going past Lega Siaka's 7
Tony Ura's 151 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for PNG), surpassing Lega Siaka's 109
Tony Ura has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (6) in ODIs for PNG, going past Mahuru Dai's 4
Tony Ura has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (76) in an innings in ODIs for PNG, going past Lega Siaka's 48
Vani Morea has scored 3 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for PNG breaking Mahuru Dai's record
Chad Soper has become the top wicket-taker for PNG in ODIs with 19 wickets, going past Norman Vanua's 18
Mahuru Dai has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (16) for PNG, going past Assad Vala
